21
00:01:13,579 --> 00:01:14,879
You couldn't be more wrong.

22
00:01:15,140 --> 00:01:20,780
A well-written business plan will include an executive summary which highlights the idea of the business in two pages or less.

23
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:27,140
Then you need to describe your company with information such as what type of legal structure it has, history, et cetera.

24
00:01:27,180 --> 00:01:28,799
Well, that seems easy enough.

25
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:29,819
