00:04:06,139 --> 00:04:07,000
Do you want to invest some money?

67
00:04:07,340 --> 00:04:08,099
Yes, for sure.

68
00:04:08,099 --> 00:04:10,400
A cupcake company, that sounds great.

69
00:04:10,759 --> 00:04:12,879
I know, but what happens if I don't sell cupcakes?

70
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:16,819
That's a problem for you because you have made a risky investment.

71
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:17,680
That's right.

72
00:04:17,860 --> 00:04:20,019
So that's what happens with investors.

73
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:29,939
