86
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:51,060
Economic means how much money do they make?

87
00:05:51,180 --> 00:05:54,379
Do they make $10,000 a year or $100,000 a year?

88
00:05:54,379 --> 00:06:03,339
And so the kind of people we want to sell my cupcakes to will change according to their socioeconomic factors.

89
00:06:03,540 --> 00:06:04,060
That's right.

90
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:10,920
So as you mentioned, socio comes from the word social or from society, so you're analyzing these factors from society.

91
00:06:11,660 --> 00:06:16,319
